column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.petror9#_r, p.dered_g, p.dered_r, s.z as z_spec, s.zErr, zmb.nvote, zmb.p_el as elliptical, zmb.p_cw as spiralclock, zmb.p_acw as spiralanticlock, zmb.p_edge as edgeon, zmb.p_dk as dontknow, zmb.p_mg as merger FROM Galaxy as p JOIN zooMonochromeBias AS zmb ON p.objid = zmb.objid JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE p.clean = # and zmb.nvote > = # and zmb.p_mg > #
